text: Lydia Zeitlhofer (18 February 1931 - 10 September 2019) was a German gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2019 deaths Category:German female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nuremberg
